Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:23.05,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}話しても　まだまだ　足りないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:30.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夕焼けが　街を染めてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:37.87,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うように　なかなか　いかない…って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:45.53,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}気づいたら　一緒に　泣いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:49.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}恋も　夢も　花も　虹も　風も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:52.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ぜんぶ掴もうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:55.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ダイジョウブ！　元気出して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:00.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私がそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:07.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今日のミス　悔やむより　今　乗り越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:10.74,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ダイジョウブ！　迷わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:16.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まだ見ぬ未来へと向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:21.87,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ずっと　歩いてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:24.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an7\fs20\fsp0}Dear My Friend every day & night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:28.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an7\fs20\fsp0}Always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:23.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}話還遠遠沒有說夠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:30.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}晚霞已染紅了街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:37.87,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}世事難都如人願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:45.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}察覺時已相依哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:49.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}戀情  夢想  鮮花  彩虹  微風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:52.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}抓緊這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:55.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒事的  打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:00.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為有我在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:07.02,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}與其悔恨今日不如放眼明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:10.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒事的  不要迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:16.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}向著未知的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:21.87,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}永遠走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.93,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,150)}某二人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.93,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,210)}新人修行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:39.93,title ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,140)}對這種事大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:39.93,title ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,215)}都會倍顯積極哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:20.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到現在還要跟志願生一起訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是為了做這種事而加入風紀委員的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:31.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一下都做不了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌棄的話  請用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:53.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…白井同學成為風紀委員已經一年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:53.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:57.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  也已經能活躍在現場當中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  像我這樣的人是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想著如果成為風紀委員的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:11.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣的我也說不定會有所改變才報名志願的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟不上訓練進度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循自己堅信的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取正確的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:24.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是成為風紀委員的心得之一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:24.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:28.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有貫徹信念的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定會有成果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:05.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他需要設置的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那裏和那裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:17.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  到現在為止都不去增設監視攝像頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:22.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所學校的風紀委員也夠悠閒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:22.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在受到損失之前意識到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:29.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出動了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:30.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在光天化日之下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是在風紀委員面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在增援來之前請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春在這裏待機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以損害私人物品兼盜竊現行犯的罪名將你逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:05.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可能不止一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有幾個人  充其量也就是些砸車窗賊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下下就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  給我放老實點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會為難…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  開溜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:35.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  初春  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我都折壽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸車窗賊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:00.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然初春還只是半吊子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:09.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前一樣在支部負責我的後方支援就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:14.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…其實我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也說過對方可能不止一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視這個的是白井同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:21.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來白井同學老是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老愛亂來老是擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以檢討書才會有增無減的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這真是聽不下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候擅自行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼時候啊  什麼時候都是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也明明可以等增援來了再行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣優柔寡斷的話就會給犯人逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就稍微反省一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:47.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去我們的約定怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得…了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:04.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  既然白井同學這樣想的話那我就不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這裏可不是休息室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…今天有正當的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:36.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘！我的補習資料  想找初春幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:39.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  初春同學的話  看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在還是先別去的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同學情緒有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初～春～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  今天是三葉草小褲褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  幸福的四葉草在哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？喂喂  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄起來哦了  這可是絕景哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春她到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟白井同學發生了些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:09.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:15.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這樣的事情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微讓她一個人靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼乾脆別做風紀委員就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著  別說這種沒責任心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:36.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員可是跟警備員並行的學園都市治安維持機關哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:36.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:36.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:39.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是能夠隨便辭退的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣放著她不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想應該沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  她們兩個有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:16.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  那麼在意的話就快點去和好不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話  初春說不定真的會討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除和你的組合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣就結束了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:34.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說明我們間的感情不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又這樣逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有逞強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和初春明明性格相差這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼組成組合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我其實也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初也沒有這個打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣遲鈍又什麼也做不到的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:57.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天的巡邏就到這裏結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼在意的問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:13.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…稍微有點事情想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:14.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都當了一年的風紀委員了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:23.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼交給我的工作都是後勤和打雜  與前輩一起的巡邏而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:29.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對成績優秀的自己卻被當作半吊子看待覺得很不滿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為我還是個小學生才會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單是年齡的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的情況是  擁有很大的潛能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:47.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻因此喜歡把所有事情都自己解決
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:51.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再稍微依靠一下身邊的人會很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  別擺著這副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為幫了那麼多忙的獎勵  買些甜點給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去取些錢來  稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是把我當作小孩子看待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  白井同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  為什麼你會在第七學區裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:28.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快成為中學生了  我來看一下學校和宿舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭呢  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我同歲麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為她比我小兩三歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學已經決定了去哪間中學了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:49.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  叫做常盤台中學的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:49.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起常盤台中學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:59.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是在學園都市裏都首屈一指的名門院校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:03.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…學園生活也想必很優雅的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上也不儘是像那樣美好的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:13.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不諳世事的有錢人  加上在校學生全部都是強能力者以上的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:13.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,328)\fs18}Level 3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:18.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集著一大幫把自己看得與眾不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面還有叫做「超電磁炮」的超能力者的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:28.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是個既傲慢又討人厭性格惡劣的女人錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對素未謀面的人虧你能說成這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來你到郵局干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:38.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:41.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:49.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人光是在注意著郵局人員的位置和視線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:50.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:56.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然隨便看別人的私人物品有點過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不是帶著什麼奇怪的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊口袋裏面有手槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是強盜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去匯報情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去做好將人群疏散的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逮捕他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想著幹傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的逮捕工作就交給警備員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種消極的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  請立即聯繫警備員…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(386,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別幹什麼奇怪的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客…客人們也安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  被搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像訓練時那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:50.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀  小菜一碟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:11.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  白癡啊  居然被一個小鬼給撂倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:14.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:18.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你們倆認識麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輕舉妄動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是風紀委員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的話應該不會棄人質於不顧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:34.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況是自己的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還有你的同伴在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要現身的話就趁現在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事  居然在這種時候鳴響警報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道客人的生命還不及金錢來的重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收防衛信號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始排除入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請繳械投降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊的口袋裏放著什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:07.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告完畢  開始執行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:25.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:29.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:36.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在摸清對手底細之前  切忌輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:46.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:52.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為能像幹掉那傻子一樣幹掉我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:58.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:03.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:11.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我輕率的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:14.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連累了初春和固法前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:20.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副狼狽樣  這不是連半吊子都不如嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  浪費我的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完沒完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:40.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會…想辦法把你救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想玩什麼把戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「空間移動」麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學  你還在裏面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:56.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只把我給送出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學也請快逃出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:07.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想逃出去  可我還無法對自己使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:12.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  事件還沒有解決呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:14.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:19.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊  求求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面有強盜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員被強盜襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們幫幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來猜猜看你在想什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警報也響了有一會兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備員也差不多該就位了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要保證人質的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功地拖住我的話就是自己的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:44.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:50.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你怎麼知道我一定無法從這裏脫身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕對等速」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Equal Speed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所投擲出的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非其本身遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是能力效果被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則無論前面出現什麼都會繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾啊  讓你白費了一番功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:23.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  用你的能力把裏面的錢轉移出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你協助我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把所有人都放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要和我合作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我聯手的話可就天下無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:35.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為第一次工作實在是太失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:44.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅擅自行動  還將大家都牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:51.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會與你為伍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我幫你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:03.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不巧  我對只知道襲擊郵局的沒出息的小賊連半點興趣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:04.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們了  來人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在此下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己所堅信的正義  決不會屈折
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:17.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼  真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種能力  空有力量卻完全沒有速度可言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要雙腿能夠聽話的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你就死在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說一次只能投擲一顆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:43.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:56.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的鐵珠和我的空間移動究竟誰快  來一決高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:56.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(284,328)\fs18}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:03.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到你能夠以一人之力將事件解決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:45.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「遵循自己堅信的正義  採取正確的行動」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會將自己堅信的正義貫徹到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論遇到什麼事都決不氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  我也會成為像白井同學那樣的風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(495,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:02.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的誓言  也請容許我借用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:07.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我一直以為可以憑一己之力解決任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:15.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你願意和我一起努力  成為獨當一面的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:21.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美好的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:31.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:37.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來所謂的約定是指那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  事到如今該怎麼道歉才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是白井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  初春她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:48.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說之前的停車場盜竊犯的藏身之處已經確定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就突然飛奔出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在那之後也一直在搜索哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:07.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「遵循自己堅信的正義  採取正確的行動」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:09.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕彼此發生些小摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要事後仍能攜手共進的話又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:37.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話  要何時才能真正一起做到「獨當一面」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:43.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會讓人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:45.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:50.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由得讓人感到  那就是青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…白井同學  你不覺得有點快過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要丟下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用空間轉移太不公平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子和初春可真是青春激盪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:33.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員可不是三兩下就能看透的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:33.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:35.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人是否也來體驗一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  姐姐大人的初體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別亂扯！

